How swift death's hand can arrive to touch any and all.  By analogy,  I guess we are all experiencing the sudden death of an illusion.  I would say the death of that poor faithful animal is more significant than the death of a vain illusion.  And, the fact that you would be the kind of person who would respond as you obviously did, out of compassion and tenderness, is a more important fact than some fucking number some Street agency is assigning to our misery in some wretched board room atop a commercial temple.   ----cgy
 

